name: Catch
long_description: Catch makes it easy for anyone who doesn't get benefits from an employer to set up and manage their own benefits package. We automatically withhold from each paycheck for tax withholding, time off, savings and retirement. We also help you find and enroll in the right health insurance plan and keep your premium payments on track. By connecting to your existing bank account, we monitor when you get paid, and act on a plan that can help keep you covered no matter what life throws at you.
